Build:

    autoreconf -vfi
    ./configure
    make
    make install

Configure options:

   --enable-gadgets / --disable-gadgets
                Enable or disable building dzen2 gadgets. Default - enabled.

   --enable-xpm / --disable-xpm
                Enable or disable XPM support. Default - auto.

   --enable-xft / --disable-xft
                Enable or disable XFT support. Default - auto.

   --enable-xcursor / --disable-xcursor
                Enable or disable XCursor support. Default - auto.

   --enable-xinerama / --disable-xinerama
                Enable or disable Xinerama support. Default - auto.

Use "./dzen2-help" to view a nicely formated version of the documentation.
